          <LEXSenses>
            <LEXSense LanguageCode="en" LastEdited="2022-02-18 12:05:28" LastEditedBy="">
              <DefinitionLong/>
              <DefinitionShort>to be under severe limitations or restrictions</DefinitionShort>
              <Glosses>
                <Gloss>to live under restrictions</Gloss>
                <Gloss>to be restricted</Gloss>
                <Gloss>to be confined</Gloss>
              </Glosses>
              <Comments>In a number of languages it may be more meaningful to render {S:04700601200004} as ‘it is not that we impose restrictions on you; it is you yourselves who are doing it.’ For another interpretation of στενοχωρέομαι in {S:04700601200004} as part of an idiom, see {D:25.54}.</Comments>
