            <LEXSense LanguageCode="en" LastEdited="2022-02-18 12:05:28" LastEditedBy="">
              <DefinitionLong/>
              <DefinitionShort>(an idiom, literally: to be restricted in the bowels) to restrict one’s affection for someone</DefinitionShort>
              <Glosses>
                <Gloss>to not respond with affection to someone</Gloss>
                <Gloss>to close one’s heart to</Gloss>
              </Glosses>
              <Comments>In {S:04700601200010} it is also possible to understand στενοχωρέομαι as meaning ‘to live with severe restrictions’ (see {D:37.18}), and σπλάγχνα may be interpreted as a psychological faculty of intent and feeling (see {D:26.11}).</Comments>
